@startuml

actor Admin
participant System
database DB

== Data Seeding ==
Admin -> System: Submit seed data\n(schools, departments, programs,\ncourses, teachers, semesters, sections)
System -> System: Validate data

alt Invalid
    System -> Admin: Notify issues
    Admin -> System: Resubmit corrected data
else Valid
    System -> DB: Save data
end

== Student Records Seeding ==
Admin -> System: Submit completed courses\n(from_admin = TRUE)
System -> DB: Save completed courses

@enduml
